<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1038123" n="1"/> 
  <opener><salute><lb/>Viro Clarissimo <add>atque</add> Celeberrimo <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119112450">Jacobo Hermanno</rs> <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119166895">NBernoull<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice></rs>.</salute></opener>
  <p><lb/><add>R</add>eddit<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sunt <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <abbr>Rev.</abbr> Domino <rs type="person">Parente</rs> Tuo <rs type="person">Patri</rs> meo <rs type="letters">liter<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> Tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, quasque iisdem pro
    <lb/>me incluseras mihi tradidit <rs type="person">Pater</rs>, qui Tibi pro officiosissima Tua <rs type="letter">responsione</rs> et
    <lb/>pro studio, quo <add>T</add>e teneri, <add>non solum ex <rs type="letter">literis</rs> Tuis sed aliunde jam satis</add> <add>ex</add>perti sumus, promoven<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>di co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>oda <rs type="person">Adgnati</rs> mei <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3164603">Venetiis</rs> nunc degentis, su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>as agit gratias, Teque quam<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>maxime rogatum cupit, ut eum porro <add>data occasione</add> officii sui admonere velis hortarique, ut
    <lb/>Tibi subinde exemplum aliquod pictur<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> su<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> mittat, si non alium in finem, saltem
    <lb/>ut sese exercendi otiumque fugiendi ansam habeat. Male certe habet <rs type="person">Patrem</rs>
    <lb/>meum, quod nullum hactenus pictur<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> su<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> exemplum Tibi miserit,
    <lb/>cum tamen Te aliquod petiisse ipsemet jam ante mensem scripserit, <add>atque</add>
    <lb/>hoc signum esse judi<add>cans</add>, eum desidi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> quam laboris amantiorem esse <add>censet</add>
    <lb/><add>cum <rs type="person">Matre</rs></add> ejus et propinquis, illum <add>quovis modo et</add> si nequeat adhortationibus, inopia et
    <lb/>parcius subministrata pecunia ad laborem adigendum esse, quorum si conatibus
    <lb/>ipse quoque aderis, obstringes quam maxime <rs type="persons">familiam</rs> nostram, pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sertim
    <lb/>quoque <rs type="person">Parentem</rs> meum, qu<unclear>e</unclear>m vicissim ad qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>vis officia nunquam
    <lb/>non habebis paratissimum. H<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c jussu <rs type="person">Patris</rs>. Quod attinet ad posthum<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
    <lb/><rs type="biblio">Opus</rs> <rs type="person">Patrui</rs> mei <choice><abbr>p. m.</abbr><expan>piae memoriae</expan></choice> scripsit mihi quidem <rs type="person">Adgnatus</rs>, se quantum per se liceat
    <lb/>libenter illud Domino <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117601020">Montmortio</rs> concessurum, sed cum <rs type="person">Mater</rs>, penes quam
    <lb/>est hic <rs type="biblio">Tractatus</rs>, non eodem sit animo, rogavi eum per <rs type="letters">literas</rs>, ut ipse cum
    <lb/><rs type="person">Matre</rs> sua hac de re ageret, ei<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> tam multum temporis diuturna
    <lb/>ista cunctatione inutiliter perdi persuaderet. De lite 
    <lb/>exorta super <rs type="biblio">dissertatione</rs> Domini <abbr>Prof.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-115793895">Battierii</rs><note type="editorial">Wortumstellung.</note>
    <lb/><hi rend="u">de Mundo</hi> non est cur aliquid dicam, cum illa
    <lb/>mox sopita fuerit morte <abbr>D.</abbr> Professoris <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-100704514">Wetstenii</rs>, qui prim<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice>
    <lb/>hanc sententiam publice fuisse defensam inique tulit, deque hac re in
    <lb/>conventu Theologico <add>grav</add>iter conquestus voluit ut Professoribus Philo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sophi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> defensio ejusmodi opinionum in posterum interdiceretur.</p>
  <pb facs="1038124" n="2"/>
  <p><lb/>Turbas tamen etiam excitavit h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c <rs type="biblio">dissertatio</rs> <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2657896">Tiguri</rs>, et occasionem dedit
    <lb/><rs type="biblio">dissertationi</rs> cuidam ridicul<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, cui Titulus <hi rend="u">Liber Natur<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></hi> <choice><orig><g ref="#pp">pp.</g></orig><reg>etc.</reg></choice> <add>quam</add> rem omn<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice>
    <lb/>sine dubio jam intellexisti ex <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-120379260">Scheuchzero</rs> juniore, qui Te, ut audivi,
    <lb/>nuper <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3171728">Patavii</rs> visitavit. Conterraneum ejus quendam, <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1036931382">Henricum Hirzeli<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs>
    <lb/>Theologi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> studiosum, qui peracto per <rs type="place" key="place_VER-belgie">Belgium</rs> et <rs type="place" key="place_KON-deutsch">Germaniam</rs> itinere lite<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rario, hi<add>c</add> <add>aliquandiu moratus est,</add> crastinaque die <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2657896">Tigurum</rs>, et inde in <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2659224">Thermas Fabarienses</rs>,
    <lb/>dehinc <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3171728">Patavium</rs> proficiscetur, ibidem Mathesi Te <rs type="person">Magistro</rs> operam
    <lb/>daturus, ut amicum Tibi co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>endare audeo, hunc si quo officio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rum genere adjuvabis, habebis et illum et me, qui Tibi jam multis nominib<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice>
    <lb/><add>sum</add> devinctus, gratissimum.</p>
  <closer><lb/><salute>Vale.</salute> <dateline><rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2661604">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <abbr>d.</abbr> <date when="1711-05-26">26. Maji 1711</date>.</dateline></closer>
</div>
